Votorantim Hires Joao Teixeira as Co-Head of Wholesale Banking

-- B y   C r i s t i a n e   L u c c h e s i
-- 
2011-07-04T14:59:57Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-07-04/votorantim-hires-joao-teixeira-as-co-head-of-wholesale-banking.html
Banco Votorantim SA hired Joao Teixeira, a former Banco Santander SA executive, to co-head its
newly created wholesale banking division along with Walter
Piacsek.  Teixeira will be responsible for corporate and investment
banking, the broker dealer unit, fixed income, derivatives and
funding, according to Sao Paulo-based Votorantim. Piacsek will
run middle market credit, asset management, private banking and
the legal department.  To contact the reporters on this story:
Cristiane Lucchesi in Sao Paulo at 
 clucchesi5@bloomberg.net   To contact the editor responsible for this story:
David Scheer at 
 dscheer@bloomberg.net  